<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīśākavarṣē nidhigajadinakṛtsaṁmitē mārgaśīrṣē paṁcamyāṁ bhānu
<lb n="2" break="no"/><unclear>vā</unclear>rē harigirinṛharēśśaṁkarāryyātmajōdāt <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīnēmagramajātasuguṇa
<lb n="3" break="no"/><unclear>dhari</unclear>yapaḥ siddhaye puṇyavṛddhyai bhaktyā kauṁḍinyagōtraḥ pratidinamama
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ḷā<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied> mālikāṁ kṛṣṇabhaṭṭaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśakavarṣaṁbulu 1289 gunēṁṭi mārga
<lb n="5" break="no"/>śira bahala paṁcamayu bhānuvāramunāṁḍu kauṁḍinyagōtrōt
<lb n="6" break="no"/>bhūtuṁḍaina nēmagrāmāna śaṁkarabhaṭṭōpādhyāyala koḍuku kṛṣṇabhaṭṭu
<lb n="7"/>tanaku saṁtānābhivṛddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhanādhuniki nityamunnu Oka tiru
<lb n="8" break="no"/>māla Atupāsi nālu mūḷu 4 cātiṁpanu bhaṭṭari pūrāIbhaṭlaku gaṁ<unclear>ḍa</unclear>mā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḷu Enimidi Icci Iṁddulōnu toṭagaṭṭu viluvanu mā 2 Unamāḍa Ā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> nitya
<lb n="10" break="no"/>munu prasādamu kuṁca ṭhāvupeṭṭi vīrikē Iccenu Ī dharmmu nāśaṁdrārka <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="11"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ṭanu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> I darmmu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrī śrī śrī
</p>

